- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper discusses the development of control software for gas turbine engines, which involves software engineering principles and practices. 
- cs.RO (Robotics): Although the paper does not explicitly mention robotics, the techniques used for control system development and verification can be applied to robotics as well. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages): The paper does not focus on programming languages, but it does mention the development of control code for the engine, which involves programming.
